---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Virtual Data Analyst - Tímový Projekt">
  <main class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>Virtual Data Analyst</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Tímový projekt - TP25/26</p>
    </header>

    <section class="project-info section">
      <h2>O projekte</h2>
      <h3>Oficiálne zadanie:</h3>
      <p class="assignment">
        GenAI-powered application that allows non-technical users to analyze and
        process their data. The application has a simple web UI where users ask
        data-related questions, such as "What is the most profitable line of
        service?", "How many records have missing values?" or even "Do we have
        some anomalies in the transaction data?". The application uses GenAI to
        understand the question and write a search query to pull relevant data
        from company databases. It may also decide to call pre-defined
        processing modules (e.g. anomaly detection). Based on the results it
        will form a respnse to the question and display it within the UI,
        optionally with some visualizations.
      </p>
      <h3>Hlavné funkcionality:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Kladenie otázok v ľudskom jazyku (napr. "Aký bol najpredávanejší
          produkt minulý rok?")
        </li>
        <li>Automatické generovanie databázových dopytov pomocou GenAI</li>
        <li>Vytváranie vizualizácií a analýz</li>
        <li>Detekcia anomálií a chýbajúcich hodnôt</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="team-info section">
      <h2>Náš tím</h2>
      <div class="team-members">
        <div class="member">
          <h4>Peter Muzslay</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="member">
          <h4>Janka Tarčáková</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="member">
          <h4>Jana Kampová</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="member">
          <h4>Jozef Guláš</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="member">
          <h4>Tamara Uhrinová</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--pwc-light);
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--pwc-gray);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .team-members {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .member {
    background: white;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--pwc-orange);
    border-left: 8px solid var(--pwc-orange);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 60px;
    min-height: 60px;
  }

  .member h4 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    color: var(--pwc-dark);
  }

  ul {
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
